kg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voguehk.com%2Fzh%2Farticle%2Ffashion%2Fsammi-cheng-september-cover-2020%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513RTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=6ad48525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voguehk.com/zh/article/fashion/sammi-cheng-september-cover-2020/</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw 以前係咁嘅樣。。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/118230638_10159003149858754_6479388454850213054_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=eEFfdesQY18AX93xc1M&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=8c7fc196c9e85eabf82190b91f413202&amp;oe=5F813020\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F118230638_10159003149858754_6479388454850213054_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DeEFfdesQY18AX93xc1M%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D8c7fc196c9e85eabf82190b91f413202%26oe%3D5F813020&h=c58e8e15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d4646fadfee118515ffaefb7f50f6e45c8d4d6c","tid":2200112,"uid":24160,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T17:02:35.000Z","msg":"Stanley: 說到愛情，去到細水長流前必然有過激情階段，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fZUQmjV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfZUQmjV.gif&h=1853f11b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但經過長時間後兩個人可能轉化為家人關係，你怎麼看愛情？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSammi: 很同意你的說法，從激情漸漸演變成細水長流的關係，這過程對我而言是很美好的。很多人會認為沒有激情便會覺得很沉悶，<br />\n<br />\n我反而會很傳統地想，能夠變成一種親人般的關係是非常難得的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/4/4b/1285375790.gif/revision/latest?cb=20100925153846\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F4b%2F1285375790.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20100925153846&h=59fe64b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n試想人生身邊有幾多人會變成你的家人，和永遠同甘共苦的人？這種關係是我夢𥧌以求的。"},{"pid":"55d28704abf745d9c92319b50a5c5dbcb2069338","tid":2200112,"uid":57996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T17:04:48.000Z","ms